WEBVTT

00:08.520 --> 00:11.150
Dou Ming's nanny
was there to care for her.

00:11.480 --> 00:12.449
She should've known

00:12.450 --> 00:14.289
whether she was pregnant.

00:14.290 --> 00:15.719
They didn't say anything at all.

00:15.720 --> 00:17.070
What were they trying to do?

00:18.330 --> 00:19.630
All this while,

00:20.230 --> 00:22.489
Ming has been busy managing
the residence's expenditure

00:22.490 --> 00:24.220
while seeking a decent position for me.

00:25.080 --> 00:26.740
Besides, she just got married.

00:26.920 --> 00:28.510
She hasn't learned much yet.

00:28.530 --> 00:30.489
Why would she risk her own child's life?

00:30.490 --> 00:32.439
She even stole her own sister's husband!

00:32.440 --> 00:33.940
What else is she not capable of?

00:34.020 --> 00:36.079
If only you married Dou Zhao instead.

00:36.080 --> 00:37.319
She'd make sure our residence

00:37.320 --> 00:39.470
would prosper for three generations!

00:39.680 --> 00:41.540
Enough! Stop that.

00:41.640 --> 00:45.070
In the end, all you care about is money.

00:45.810 --> 00:47.540
Anyway, I hope
that you'll stop interfering

00:48.280 --> 00:49.860
in the residence's matters.

00:52.280 --> 00:53.679
That wretched lass

00:53.680 --> 00:55.300
must have bewitched you

00:55.810 --> 00:58.279
that you don't even listen to me.

00:58.280 --> 00:59.420
You...

01:00.410 --> 01:02.030
Mind yourself, Your Ladyship.

01:05.960 --> 01:07.190
What did you call me?

01:08.680 --> 01:10.340
They say an elder sister
is like a mother.

01:11.400 --> 01:12.590
All these years,

01:13.320 --> 01:16.670
I've been managing
the household for you.

01:18.810 --> 01:20.390
Now that you have a wife,

01:20.910 --> 01:21.889
you've totally forgotten

01:21.890 --> 01:23.929
everything I've done for you!

01:23.930 --> 01:25.690
Stop claiming
that you're doing this for me!

01:26.830 --> 01:27.679
I can see

01:27.680 --> 01:29.500
that you've been unhappy over the years

01:30.200 --> 01:31.590
in the Duke of Jing's Residence.

01:32.600 --> 01:34.030
I feel for you.

01:35.290 --> 01:36.980
If you could,

01:37.170 --> 01:38.590
please put yourself in Ming's shoes.

01:40.320 --> 01:41.500
From now on,

01:43.810 --> 01:45.750
stop worrying about the affairs here.

01:53.310 --> 01:56.050
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

01:56.460 --> 01:58.870
If I were as capable as my sister,

01:59.300 --> 02:00.950
I wouldn't have been in this state.

02:01.280 --> 02:02.540
Ming, it's not like that.

02:02.650 --> 02:03.790
You know

02:03.930 --> 02:06.470
what kind of person I am, don't you?

02:06.930 --> 02:08.470
I thought I knew you.

02:09.360 --> 02:11.079
But, your sister said...

02:11.080 --> 02:12.270
I know.

02:13.410 --> 02:16.639
In the end, all my sister
and your mother wanted

02:16.640 --> 02:18.660
was just money and material comforts.

02:19.360 --> 02:22.150
Since that's the case,
I'll just work hard and earn them

02:22.730 --> 02:25.380
so that we can enjoy
some peace and quiet.

02:25.450 --> 02:26.660
You have an idea?

02:27.200 --> 02:29.270
Many people are eager to buy my artwork,

02:29.970 --> 02:32.060
but they were all lowly
and crude commoners,

02:32.200 --> 02:34.030
so I refused to have
anything to do with them.

02:35.890 --> 02:37.620
You are an excellent artist.

02:38.170 --> 02:39.870
If you're willing to sell to the public,

02:39.920 --> 02:42.900
people would flock over
to buy your artwork.

02:42.910 --> 02:44.470
If you make a name in the art industry,

02:44.480 --> 02:46.470
your artwork will be immortalized.

02:47.600 --> 02:49.220
That's your dream too, right?

02:51.890 --> 02:53.500
Things will get better for us.

02:54.760 --> 02:55.990
For you, Ming.

04:18.910 --> 04:23.109
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

04:23.110 --> 04:26.370
=Episode 22=

04:30.510 --> 04:32.240
Madam, you've gone through
so much trouble

04:32.250 --> 04:33.910
to secure a job for the Duke,

04:34.160 --> 04:35.870
yet he refused to accept it.

04:36.160 --> 04:38.790
He'd rather sell his artwork
to the lowly commoners.

04:38.930 --> 04:40.079
How could our young mistress

04:40.080 --> 04:41.809
marry such a useless man?

04:41.810 --> 04:43.060
Mind your tongue.

04:43.490 --> 04:44.700
Even so,

04:45.050 --> 04:46.620
he's my son-in-law.

04:47.490 --> 04:48.910
No matter what,

04:49.050 --> 04:51.550
I'll eke out a path for Ming

04:52.080 --> 04:54.430
and make sure
she doesn't repeat my past.

04:57.450 --> 04:58.700
What's going on?

05:03.080 --> 05:04.199
Madam.

05:04.200 --> 05:05.460
Long time no see.

05:06.710 --> 05:09.770
(Jieyi Hall)

05:18.500 --> 05:20.580
Your father has been
waging war against us bandits.

05:20.840 --> 05:22.750
Why didn't you send us a letter?

05:23.130 --> 05:26.129
We've been earning money
for you over the years.

05:26.130 --> 05:27.910
Are you trying to get rid of us?

05:29.130 --> 05:30.500
Of course not.

05:30.590 --> 05:32.750
We've just had two marriages
in the residence lately,

05:33.100 --> 05:35.580
so I was too busy to talk
to my father about this.

05:36.470 --> 05:37.610
Madam.

05:37.630 --> 05:39.490
Are you trying to fool us?

05:40.390 --> 05:42.770
If you keep this foolery up,

05:44.550 --> 05:46.930
you'd have a taste of my blade!

05:55.790 --> 05:56.930
Come on.

05:56.950 --> 05:58.090
Slaughter me!

05:58.550 --> 06:01.730
I hope that makes you and I happy.

06:02.990 --> 06:03.949
Madam.

06:03.950 --> 06:05.690
- What are you saying?
- Shut up!

06:07.870 --> 06:09.010
You can

06:10.270 --> 06:12.290
end my life now.

06:12.870 --> 06:14.250
Let's see if my father,

06:15.270 --> 06:17.570
the Minister of War,

06:17.870 --> 06:20.010
will let you guys off.

06:22.030 --> 06:23.170
Otherwise,

06:23.790 --> 06:25.650
you'd better untie me,

06:26.630 --> 06:28.570
so we can sit and talk.

06:33.350 --> 06:34.229
Guys!

06:34.230 --> 06:35.370
Yes, sir!

06:36.120 --> 06:37.770
Untie her.

06:47.790 --> 06:53.049
(Jieyi Hall)

06:53.050 --> 06:54.190
Madam.

06:55.340 --> 06:56.480
Pardon me.

06:57.510 --> 06:59.949
As you know, all of us

06:59.950 --> 07:01.570
are just trying to make a living.

07:01.830 --> 07:04.109
If you have the money
to support your daughter,

07:04.110 --> 07:06.210
then what about the debt you owe us?

07:06.390 --> 07:07.629
At this rate,

07:07.630 --> 07:09.349
my brothers might get hungry

07:09.350 --> 07:11.690
and rob the Duke of Jining's residence

07:12.070 --> 07:13.410
for a change.

07:16.990 --> 07:18.570
All the Duke of Jining has now

07:18.790 --> 07:21.650
are just debt and pawn tickets.

07:21.840 --> 07:23.690
If you don't believe me,
go ahead and rob them.

07:24.350 --> 07:25.650
If you ask me,

07:26.460 --> 07:29.330
if you really want to go all out,

07:30.450 --> 07:32.930
there's another residence you can rob.

07:36.950 --> 07:40.130
(Jieyi Hall)

07:47.710 --> 07:48.850
Come here.

07:49.490 --> 07:50.630
What is it?

07:52.030 --> 07:53.170
Stand here.

07:53.990 --> 07:55.130
Close your eyes.

07:55.580 --> 07:56.810
Close your eyes.

07:57.910 --> 07:59.050
What's going on?

07:59.940 --> 08:01.170
Don't peek.

08:10.310 --> 08:11.530
What are you doing?

08:12.310 --> 08:13.450
Don't move.

08:17.390 --> 08:18.530
Almost there.

08:25.510 --> 08:29.069
Isn't it more appropriate
to do this at night instead?

08:29.070 --> 08:30.490
Why can't we do it in the day?

08:30.500 --> 08:32.340
In fact, it's better
since you can see clearer

08:32.350 --> 08:33.570
when there's ample lighting.

08:56.790 --> 08:58.050
Are you feeling hot?

08:58.110 --> 08:59.570
Why are you sweating?

09:00.110 --> 09:01.250
No.

09:01.510 --> 09:03.530
I don't feel hot.

09:04.680 --> 09:05.820
And it's done.

09:05.870 --> 09:07.010
It's done?

09:09.790 --> 09:10.930
Surprised?

09:17.910 --> 09:19.050
Surprised.

09:20.310 --> 09:22.250
You made this for me?

09:23.430 --> 09:25.250
I just wanted to measure this on you.

09:25.510 --> 09:26.730
It fits you.

09:31.230 --> 09:32.450
I thought...

09:36.470 --> 09:37.770
I was thinking too much.

09:38.390 --> 09:40.069
When I bathed you that day,

09:40.070 --> 09:42.349
I noticed a lot of wounds on your body

09:42.350 --> 09:44.570
created by the friction
caused by ill-fitted armor.

09:44.670 --> 09:46.970
Now that you're guarding
the imperial palace,

09:47.270 --> 09:49.490
you could use a golden armored vest.

09:49.750 --> 09:52.509
This will defend you from attacks

09:52.510 --> 09:54.250
without scraping your skin.

09:54.350 --> 09:55.490
It can keep you safe.

09:58.750 --> 10:01.410
What's wrong? You don't like it?

10:02.870 --> 10:04.010
I love it.

10:15.150 --> 10:18.050
You've been sighing at the vest

10:18.150 --> 10:20.050
for an hour, Your Lordship.

10:20.470 --> 10:22.530
Is there anything wrong with it?

10:23.590 --> 10:26.039
I saw how my uncle,
the Duke of Ding, and his wife

10:26.040 --> 10:28.970
remained affectionate even though
they were at the battlefield.

10:32.030 --> 10:35.290
They have always been a loving couple.

10:36.670 --> 10:39.370
What do you think of me and Dou Zhao?

10:39.390 --> 10:40.770
Do we seem different?

10:43.010 --> 10:45.770
Her Ladyship is brave and witty.

10:45.910 --> 10:48.749
She's been managing
the household efficiently.

10:48.750 --> 10:50.730
Ever since she married
into the residence,

10:51.070 --> 10:52.749
even the Duke is cautious around her,

10:52.750 --> 10:55.370
and he's stopped picking
any fights with you.

10:55.390 --> 10:57.970
She is the perfect wife for you.

11:03.750 --> 11:05.290
I have a feeling that she

11:06.230 --> 11:07.410
doesn't love me.

11:11.350 --> 11:12.269
Your Lordship.

11:12.270 --> 11:14.369
She's done so much for you

11:14.370 --> 11:16.570
and even made this vest herself.

11:17.190 --> 11:19.029
How could you say that
she doesn't love you?

11:19.030 --> 11:20.170
Exactly.

11:21.590 --> 11:22.730
No.

11:22.890 --> 11:24.730
That's not the kind of love I meant.

11:25.150 --> 11:27.810
As I told Dou Zhao,

11:28.090 --> 11:29.509
we'd face every challenge together.

11:29.510 --> 11:31.250
The way she treats me

11:31.590 --> 11:33.450
is like a strategist advising a general,

11:33.910 --> 11:35.349
just like how you're treating me.

11:35.350 --> 11:36.610
That's not love.

11:36.950 --> 11:37.949
Your Lordship.

11:37.950 --> 11:39.490
I love you.

11:39.750 --> 11:40.909
I love you too.

11:40.910 --> 11:42.029
No, no!

11:42.030 --> 11:43.770
That's not what I meant.

11:43.950 --> 11:45.690
The love Dou Zhao has for me

11:45.790 --> 11:47.389
is not romantic love.

11:47.390 --> 11:48.570
Do you understand?

11:52.870 --> 11:55.570
I am unmarried,

11:56.110 --> 11:57.810
so I don't really understand.

11:58.790 --> 12:01.890
Don't you like the way
Her Ladyship treats you?

12:02.990 --> 12:04.170
Not exactly.

12:07.030 --> 12:10.050
I'd say she's oblivious.

12:10.470 --> 12:12.090
You're getting close. Continue.

12:12.110 --> 12:13.229
Your Lordship.

12:13.230 --> 12:15.509
I'm just 17 years old,

12:15.510 --> 12:17.080
and I'm not in a romantic relationship,

12:17.190 --> 12:19.730
so I don't know what else to say.

12:20.910 --> 12:23.090
What do you kids know about love?

12:23.150 --> 12:24.149
I don't know about love?

12:24.150 --> 12:25.789
You're already this old
and still unmarried.

12:25.790 --> 12:26.669
How dare you tease me?

12:26.670 --> 12:27.519
So what?

12:27.520 --> 12:29.770
That's because my life
is dedicated to His Lordship.

12:46.990 --> 12:48.170
Yantang.

12:48.670 --> 12:51.090
Are you sure you don't want
to visit Drunken Bordello?

12:53.230 --> 12:54.570
I heard

12:54.630 --> 12:57.450
that they've hired
a bunch of pretty musicians.

12:57.990 --> 13:02.210
You can dine and wine
while listening to music.

13:03.590 --> 13:04.730
My treat.

13:05.150 --> 13:06.149
Come on.

13:06.150 --> 13:08.549
I also heard that they've also hired

13:08.550 --> 13:10.340
some handsome singers.

13:10.350 --> 13:12.190
Are you trying to emulate
the Eldest Princess?

13:12.990 --> 13:14.450
You're so petty.

13:16.990 --> 13:18.330
I got it.

13:19.030 --> 13:21.330
You're jealous.

13:25.790 --> 13:27.370
You're drunk.

13:27.470 --> 13:28.610
I'm not.

13:44.990 --> 13:46.789
Why choose such a song?

13:46.790 --> 13:48.249
Don't you know?

13:48.250 --> 13:49.989
This is what we call romance.

13:49.990 --> 13:52.150
What do you expect them to do,
recite classical texts?

13:54.910 --> 13:56.530
It seems to be working, though.

13:57.270 --> 13:58.810
What a beautiful night.

13:59.430 --> 14:00.850
Nice singing!

14:01.350 --> 14:04.210
That doesn't look very gentlemanly.

14:04.310 --> 14:06.869
You deserve to remain single forever.

14:06.870 --> 14:08.290
What's wrong with being single?

14:08.510 --> 14:09.549
I like it.

14:09.550 --> 14:12.010
You two seem to be plotting something.

14:12.350 --> 14:13.269
Spill the beans.

14:13.270 --> 14:15.370
What kind of trick
did you pull on Her Ladyship?

14:19.230 --> 14:20.820
It's not just your room.

14:20.830 --> 14:22.240
This place is filled with stars too.

14:22.250 --> 14:23.090
See?

14:33.710 --> 14:37.490
I used to loathe your eyes,

14:38.870 --> 14:40.989
but now...

14:40.990 --> 14:43.250
What now?

14:46.750 --> 14:48.410
There's a cluster of stars

14:48.470 --> 14:51.050
inside your eyes,

14:52.070 --> 14:53.890
twinkling and shining.

14:53.990 --> 14:55.290
How beautiful.

15:01.990 --> 15:03.130
Look.

15:04.070 --> 15:05.589
The reflection on the water

15:05.590 --> 15:08.050
looks so ethereal and pretty.

15:08.270 --> 15:11.410
You can see it, but you can't touch it.

15:12.990 --> 15:14.130
It's prettier this way.

15:20.670 --> 15:21.890
Do you like it?

15:25.190 --> 15:27.570
I love it.

15:29.150 --> 15:30.290
I love it.

15:32.790 --> 15:34.890
I love you too.

15:43.350 --> 15:44.490
Look.

15:45.750 --> 15:47.450
The lights are so beautiful,

15:48.030 --> 15:50.770
just like your eyes.

16:16.400 --> 16:17.540
Your Lordship!

16:22.280 --> 16:23.420
Your Lordship.

16:24.460 --> 16:25.600
Shh.

16:26.670 --> 16:27.890
Go back first

16:28.150 --> 16:30.170
and prepare some warm soup
and ginger tea for her.

16:30.510 --> 16:31.980
- I'll be back soon.
- Your Lordship.

16:32.070 --> 16:33.620
There are so many people out here.

16:33.630 --> 16:34.949
If you carry Her Ladyship back...

16:34.950 --> 16:36.500
If you don't prepare everything I asked,

16:36.510 --> 16:38.390
I'll make you run ten li
with weights tomorrow.

16:38.870 --> 16:40.010
Yes, Your Lordship.

16:40.150 --> 16:41.290
Come on.

16:51.240 --> 16:52.580
That lamp

16:53.470 --> 16:55.050
is so pretty.

16:55.950 --> 16:58.290
I'll get it for you.

16:58.810 --> 17:00.970
I'll get you whatever you want.

17:06.470 --> 17:08.469
My dad said you have no shame.

17:08.470 --> 17:09.890
I'm so sorry.

17:10.350 --> 17:12.420
- Don't blabber.
- As long as my wife is happy,

17:12.590 --> 17:13.830
I don't mind.

17:18.490 --> 17:20.990
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

17:21.160 --> 17:23.210
♪Standing side by side with you♪

17:23.220 --> 17:28.000
♪Looking at this kaleidoscopic world♪

17:31.150 --> 17:32.290
Yantang.

17:37.190 --> 17:38.690
Yantang.

17:39.170 --> 17:44.880
♪Ignoring everyone's worldly advice♪

17:45.460 --> 17:51.520
♪My love is clear as the moon,
without a hint of lie♪

17:52.330 --> 17:57.640
♪Every step I tirelessly take
gets me closer to you♪

17:57.700 --> 18:01.289
♪I devote my life and world
to your wishes♪

18:01.290 --> 18:04.610
I shouldn't take advantage of you
when you're drunk.

18:06.390 --> 18:09.020
♪Time bends and breaks♪

18:10.030 --> 18:11.850
I'll let you off tonight.

18:19.310 --> 18:20.450
Yantang.

18:20.750 --> 18:23.879
Actually, I'm not drunk.

18:23.880 --> 18:28.649
♪My heart has room only for one,
filled to the brim♪

18:28.650 --> 18:31.420
♪I know that relationships♪

18:31.760 --> 18:34.160
♪Can be hard to decipher♪

18:35.990 --> 18:38.810
(Natural Grace and Talent)

18:39.160 --> 18:41.980
♪Without regret♪

18:46.270 --> 18:47.500
You're awake, Your Ladyship.

18:55.920 --> 18:56.859
Don't worry.

18:56.860 --> 18:58.150
I changed your clothes.

18:59.980 --> 19:01.239
As for your hangover soup,

19:01.240 --> 19:03.650
it was His Lordship who made it for you.

19:07.550 --> 19:09.890
You were absolutely
intoxicated last night.

19:11.150 --> 19:13.530
I do seem to have a memory lapse.

19:15.150 --> 19:18.470
I only remember that last night,

19:18.980 --> 19:21.330
we went to enjoy some performances,

19:21.470 --> 19:22.890
and...

19:24.130 --> 19:25.270
And what happened?

19:25.550 --> 19:28.330
You'll have to ask His Lordship.

19:28.640 --> 19:30.760
You were hugging him the whole night.

19:30.790 --> 19:32.390
When he left the room this morning,

19:32.400 --> 19:34.390
his neck was purplish
from the constant gripping.

19:34.400 --> 19:36.370
That's why you'll have to ask him.

19:59.190 --> 20:00.330
You're awake.

20:01.230 --> 20:02.920
I thought you'd sleep in.

20:03.230 --> 20:04.470
Last night...

20:04.770 --> 20:05.910
Yantang.

20:08.240 --> 20:09.870
Last night,

20:11.650 --> 20:14.330
I got greedy and drank too much.

20:16.390 --> 20:18.090
Other than that,

20:18.450 --> 20:20.570
I didn't do anything
inappropriate, did I?

20:21.600 --> 20:22.740
Other than what?

20:22.930 --> 20:24.160
What are they saying?

20:24.750 --> 20:27.130
I guess it's nothing.

20:27.310 --> 20:28.810
I mean,

20:29.900 --> 20:32.730
I didn't get rowdy
after drinking, did I?

20:35.710 --> 20:37.349
You've always been calm and composed.

20:37.350 --> 20:38.490
Of course, you didn't.

20:40.190 --> 20:42.610
All you did was tugging me

20:43.270 --> 20:44.869
to watch the lights and stars together.

20:44.870 --> 20:46.709
Then, you pointed at random things
and asked me to buy them.

20:46.710 --> 20:48.900
You also hugged me the entire night
and babbled a bunch of stuff.

20:48.910 --> 20:50.869
Don't take my words seriously

20:50.870 --> 20:52.090
when I'm drunk.

20:53.020 --> 20:56.699
So, you didn't mean it
when you said my eyes

20:56.700 --> 20:57.840
were gentle and pretty?

20:59.610 --> 21:01.930
You said you love...

21:02.190 --> 21:03.429
Yantang.

21:03.430 --> 21:05.890
You should go to work now.

21:06.030 --> 21:07.570
- It's getting late, go.
- Sure.

21:08.820 --> 21:09.729
By the way,

21:09.730 --> 21:11.290
I put the lamp at the front yard.

21:15.900 --> 21:17.209
This lamp...

21:17.210 --> 21:18.319
His Lordship

21:18.320 --> 21:20.269
got Mr. Yan to bring it back last night.

21:20.270 --> 21:23.050
You even wanted to bring it back
to your room and hug it to sleep.

21:26.310 --> 21:29.050
That lamp is so pretty.

21:30.030 --> 21:31.170
Sure.

21:31.230 --> 21:33.410
I'll get you whatever you want.

21:34.150 --> 21:35.290
Your Ladyship!

21:35.430 --> 21:36.789
- No, Your Ladyship!
- Push it in!

21:36.790 --> 21:38.130
- Come on!
- Stop it, please!

21:39.260 --> 21:41.109
It was the Duke of Jing
from the South Warden

21:41.110 --> 21:42.669
who commissioned this lamp

21:42.670 --> 21:44.300
for the old duchess's birthday.

21:44.600 --> 21:45.469
It's 100 cun tall,

21:45.470 --> 21:47.299
which symbolizes a long life.

21:47.300 --> 21:48.610
Do you like it?

21:49.430 --> 21:51.330
I do like it,

21:51.430 --> 21:53.069
but I'm literally
taking her long life...

21:53.070 --> 21:53.949
No,

21:53.950 --> 21:56.650
I mean, I'm taking her birthday gift.

21:56.830 --> 21:58.210
That doesn't seem appropriate.

21:58.390 --> 21:59.509
It's fine.

21:59.510 --> 22:02.389
His Lordship has already
commissioned a new lamp for her.

22:02.390 --> 22:03.930
As long as you like it.

22:08.030 --> 22:09.610
So, Your Ladyship.

22:09.630 --> 22:12.370
Shall we hang the lamp?

22:13.630 --> 22:15.010
This lamp looks too gaudy.

22:15.150 --> 22:16.429
Hang it at the back gate.

22:16.430 --> 22:17.269
Yes, Your Ladyship.

22:17.270 --> 22:20.530
(Fleeting Time)

22:21.870 --> 22:23.210
Maybe we should put it back in.

22:27.710 --> 22:29.050
Nice.

22:30.730 --> 22:33.530
Not many people in the capital

22:33.700 --> 22:36.009
is capable of drawing cranes

22:36.010 --> 22:37.670
in such a vivid manner.

22:37.970 --> 22:39.370
It's spectacular.

22:40.030 --> 22:42.850
I can offer 1,000 taels.

22:46.380 --> 22:47.829
My husband has created

22:47.830 --> 22:49.109
thousands of paintings,

22:49.110 --> 22:51.730
and this is his best one.

22:52.200 --> 22:55.630
Still, you need to make
a few adjustments.

22:56.230 --> 22:58.949
First, the background.

22:58.950 --> 23:00.170
Instead of the mountains,

23:00.230 --> 23:02.820
you should draw the fields instead.

23:04.150 --> 23:05.290
The fields?

23:05.390 --> 23:06.699
Cranes are noble creatures

23:06.700 --> 23:07.930
that dwell in the mountains.

23:08.530 --> 23:10.100
How could it exist in the fields?

23:11.470 --> 23:14.660
I'm planning to gift this to Lord Chen.

23:14.670 --> 23:16.390
He's crippled,

23:16.590 --> 23:18.339
and seeing these mountains

23:18.340 --> 23:19.810
would only upset him.

23:20.790 --> 23:23.170
Cranes in the fields
sound like a fun idea too.

23:23.180 --> 23:26.690
The feathers look too simplistic.

23:26.750 --> 23:28.029
They should look fuller

23:28.030 --> 23:30.660
so that the painting looks valuable.

23:30.700 --> 23:33.890
Also, the crane's head looks too faded.

23:34.230 --> 23:35.040
It's not...

23:35.050 --> 23:37.419
Since you don't understand art,
I shall not sell it to you.

23:37.420 --> 23:38.860
I'll only sell to those
who can understand.

23:38.870 --> 23:40.429
This…This is my first time seeing

23:40.430 --> 23:42.219
someone who refuses to negotiate a deal!

23:42.220 --> 23:44.029
I'm so sorry, Mr. Zhou.

23:44.030 --> 23:47.050
Perhaps this deal is over,
but there's still next time.

23:49.310 --> 23:50.949
At least the duchess is sensible.

23:50.950 --> 23:54.330
You're beautiful and courteous.

23:55.120 --> 23:56.569
You lecher!

23:56.570 --> 23:57.449
- Men!
- Yes, Your Lordship!

23:57.450 --> 23:58.519
Shoo this man away, now!

23:58.520 --> 23:59.409
- Yes, Your Lordship!
- Tingyu!

23:59.410 --> 24:00.349
- Your Lordship!
- Don't!

24:00.350 --> 24:01.469
What did I do wrong?

24:01.470 --> 24:02.890
- Tingyu!
- Move it!

24:03.030 --> 24:04.269
What's wrong with you?

24:04.270 --> 24:05.399
- Move it!
- Your Lordship!

24:05.400 --> 24:06.540
Get out!

24:09.500 --> 24:10.629
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

24:10.630 --> 24:11.930
Unhand me!

24:12.110 --> 24:13.410
- Run along!
- Run along!

24:14.870 --> 24:16.010
You all...

24:19.390 --> 24:20.730
1,000 taels

24:20.950 --> 24:22.970
is one year's worth
of our food expenses.

24:23.550 --> 24:25.229
He may be just an art dealer,

24:25.230 --> 24:27.119
but many artists became famous
because of him.

24:27.120 --> 24:28.260
He might be able

24:28.300 --> 24:30.330
to sell your artwork to collectors

24:30.350 --> 24:31.209
and even the palace.

24:31.210 --> 24:32.279
Ming.

24:32.280 --> 24:33.629
Art is a spiritual pursuit

24:33.630 --> 24:34.669
that expresses one's mind.

24:34.670 --> 24:36.080
If I paint things
that go against my principles

24:36.090 --> 24:36.869
just to earn money,

24:36.870 --> 24:38.470
it'd be an insult to my brushes.

24:39.800 --> 24:41.470
If you don't want
to insult your brushes,

24:41.780 --> 24:44.560
then you might as well work
in the Military Command.

24:44.910 --> 24:46.259
Given your status as a duke,

24:46.260 --> 24:49.109
you'll make a name for yourself
and enjoy an illustrious career.

24:49.110 --> 24:50.690
My identity as a duke

24:51.000 --> 24:53.010
has made me a subject of ridicule
among my peers.

24:53.040 --> 24:54.890
Now, I even have to rely
on my wife's family.

24:56.270 --> 24:57.410
I don't care

24:57.790 --> 24:58.930
about this position.

24:59.270 --> 25:01.069
That's because you've just started.

25:01.070 --> 25:02.770
It's normal to make mistakes.

25:02.830 --> 25:04.669
Next time, we can treat your peers

25:04.670 --> 25:05.909
to a meal at Drunken Bordello

25:05.910 --> 25:07.610
to win their support.

25:08.030 --> 25:09.650
They've been ridiculing me,

25:09.810 --> 25:12.399
and you want me to treat
those crude, uncivilized barbarians?

25:12.400 --> 25:13.850
What an insult!

25:16.630 --> 25:17.770
Fine.

25:18.310 --> 25:19.850
Since you care about your dignity,

25:20.430 --> 25:21.569
I'll do it for you.

25:21.570 --> 25:25.689
I'll make some embroidery items
and sell them,

25:25.690 --> 25:27.749
then rent a stall and sell some snacks.

25:27.750 --> 25:29.130
It doesn't matter

25:29.340 --> 25:30.339
who the breadwinner is.

25:30.340 --> 25:31.610
No way.

25:31.640 --> 25:32.580
You are a duchess.

25:32.590 --> 25:34.269
If you associate yourself
with the public,

25:34.270 --> 25:35.890
everyone in the Capital
will laugh at me!

25:35.900 --> 25:37.330
Don't you learn from your mother.

25:41.190 --> 25:42.490
What's wrong with my mother?

25:43.110 --> 25:44.970
She may have done many wrong things,

25:45.030 --> 25:46.309
but she sold congee in the past

25:46.310 --> 25:47.989
to support her entire family.

25:47.990 --> 25:49.330
What's wrong with that?

25:51.490 --> 25:52.650
Ming.

25:53.390 --> 25:54.329
Ming.

25:54.330 --> 25:55.470
I...

25:56.150 --> 25:57.410
That's not what I meant.

26:01.710 --> 26:02.850
Fine.

26:02.870 --> 26:04.070
I'll do it.

26:04.250 --> 26:05.850
I'll go back to work.

26:06.630 --> 26:08.530
(Natural Grace and Talent)

26:08.750 --> 26:09.890
Your Lordship.

26:10.550 --> 26:13.290
An old servant from the main residence
is requesting an audience.

26:16.210 --> 26:17.350
Bring him in.

26:25.310 --> 26:26.450
Your Lordship.

26:26.790 --> 26:30.640
I'm Ma Qiang, a former stableman
at the Duke of Ying's Residence.

26:31.370 --> 26:33.810
I didn't see you
when I was investigating

26:33.820 --> 26:35.580
the mass resignation
of servants back then.

26:36.030 --> 26:37.730
Why have you come now?

26:38.650 --> 26:40.890
I didn't dare to show myself

26:41.390 --> 26:42.970
because I was scared.

26:43.640 --> 26:44.869
Now, I'm here

26:44.870 --> 26:46.529
for my wife, Qi Xia.

26:46.530 --> 26:47.670
She...

26:48.430 --> 26:50.530
She used to be
the late Duchess's servant.

26:56.270 --> 26:57.410
Where's my wife?

26:57.430 --> 26:58.570
At the bookstore.

26:59.110 --> 27:00.490
Call her back, now.

27:00.550 --> 27:01.690
Yes, Your Lordship.

27:06.350 --> 27:09.549
Most of the Duchess's servants
are already gone.

27:09.550 --> 27:12.170
Qi Xia used to be one
of her personal maids.

27:12.390 --> 27:13.890
After she went mad,

27:14.030 --> 27:16.090
they assigned her to work
in the kitchen instead.

27:16.190 --> 27:18.010
That's how she escaped death.

27:18.430 --> 27:20.009
I reckon you can't get

27:20.010 --> 27:22.709
much information from her.

27:22.710 --> 27:25.170
Eagle. Cockerel.

27:27.870 --> 27:30.829
Miss, do you still remember
the Duke of Ying's Residence?

27:30.830 --> 27:32.730
Eagle. Cockerel.

27:32.830 --> 27:34.090
Of course I do.

27:34.590 --> 27:35.509
Eagle.

27:35.510 --> 27:37.150
- Time to take your medicine.
- Cockerel.

27:37.180 --> 27:38.109
Eagle.

27:38.110 --> 27:39.389
- Qi Xia.
- Cockerel.

27:39.390 --> 27:40.469
Qi Xia, come on.

27:40.470 --> 27:41.610
Drink your medicine.

27:42.110 --> 27:43.250
Eagle.

27:44.150 --> 27:44.989
I know that place.

27:44.990 --> 27:45.869
Yes, you do.

27:45.870 --> 27:46.869
- Eagle.
- Come on.

27:46.870 --> 27:48.130
Cockerel.

27:48.430 --> 27:49.570
Here you go.

27:50.670 --> 27:51.810
Don't drink it!

27:52.150 --> 27:53.370
Don't drink it!

27:53.510 --> 27:54.970
Don't drink it!

27:55.210 --> 27:57.189
- Why is she reacting strongly?
- Don't drink it!

27:57.190 --> 27:58.570
That's how it's been

27:58.670 --> 28:01.290
ever since she went crazy.

28:01.430 --> 28:03.090
Is it because
the medicine is too bitter?

28:11.300 --> 28:12.429
- It's poisonous!
- Qi Xia!

28:12.430 --> 28:13.670
- It's poisonous!
- It's not!

28:13.790 --> 28:14.879
- It's poisonous!
- Qi Xia!

28:14.880 --> 28:15.829
- It's poisonous!
- It's not!

28:15.830 --> 28:17.349
- Qi Xia!
- It's poisonous!

28:17.350 --> 28:18.669
- There, there.
- It's poisonous!

28:18.670 --> 28:19.909
- How is licorice poisonous?
- Qi Xia!

28:19.910 --> 28:20.749
It's poisonous!

28:20.750 --> 28:22.500
- Has she always been averse to it?
- It's poisonous!

28:22.510 --> 28:23.359
No.

28:23.360 --> 28:25.229
- This licorice is sweet.
- It's poisonous!

28:25.230 --> 28:26.459
- It's also good for health.
- It's poisonous!

28:26.460 --> 28:29.109
- She loved infusing licorice in water.
- It's poisonous!

28:29.110 --> 28:30.250
Can you recall

28:30.260 --> 28:32.990
- when she started resisting licorice?
- It's poisonous!

28:33.570 --> 28:34.519
I think

28:34.520 --> 28:36.880
since the late Duchess fell ill.

28:37.910 --> 28:39.050
There, there, Qi Xia.

28:39.190 --> 28:40.109
There, there.

28:40.110 --> 28:42.690
- Only my mother's maids could access
- It's poisonous!

28:42.750 --> 28:44.130
my mother's food and medicine.

28:45.270 --> 28:46.410
Could it be...

28:47.790 --> 28:48.930
Meirui?

28:49.310 --> 28:50.730
I've checked all the storerooms,

28:50.740 --> 28:52.530
kitchens, and apothecaries
in the residence.

28:53.030 --> 28:55.520
There's no licorice left in stock.

28:56.030 --> 28:57.250
I'm not an expert in medicine.

28:57.450 --> 28:59.170
Do you have any physician friends?

28:59.830 --> 29:01.410
It's only been a year since I returned.

29:01.590 --> 29:02.730
I don't trust anyone.

29:06.550 --> 29:07.690
There's one.

29:16.390 --> 29:17.770
It's a good prescription.

29:18.070 --> 29:20.930
Euphorbia is a key component

29:21.070 --> 29:23.530
in curing urinary retention.

29:23.950 --> 29:26.969
However, euphorbia
and licorice are contradictory.

29:26.970 --> 29:28.250
If taken together,

29:29.040 --> 29:30.650
it may lead to death.

29:32.160 --> 29:33.049
After my mother died,

29:33.050 --> 29:34.930
I've checked the
remnants of her medicine.

29:35.000 --> 29:37.550
They follow the prescription perfectly,
and no licorice is added.

29:38.830 --> 29:41.409
However, these symptoms
would only appear

29:41.410 --> 29:42.930
when both herbs are taken together.

29:43.870 --> 29:46.130
Perhaps licorice wasn't
added to the medicine.

29:46.750 --> 29:48.630
Does your mother have
any special food likings?

29:50.100 --> 29:51.490
My mother doesn't like bitter food,

29:51.500 --> 29:53.980
so she'd always eat some
candied fruit after taking medicine.

29:56.790 --> 29:59.010
She gave me this
before I left for Futing.

30:08.710 --> 30:09.789
That's it.

30:09.790 --> 30:11.730
This wasn't preserved in honey,

30:11.910 --> 30:13.669
but boiled in a licorice solution

30:13.670 --> 30:14.869
to infuse sweetness into it.

30:14.870 --> 30:16.290
If eaten daily,

30:16.310 --> 30:17.570
she'd die in a month.

30:18.590 --> 30:19.730
Who gave her this?

30:27.330 --> 30:28.470
Your Ladyship.

30:29.610 --> 30:30.750
Over here.

30:33.540 --> 30:35.650
She used to be the late Duchess's maid.

30:35.790 --> 30:38.330
She's gone mad now, so we can't
get any information from her.

30:38.630 --> 30:40.650
Do you think you can cure her?

30:49.790 --> 30:50.930
No.

30:51.190 --> 30:53.930
No, no.

30:56.510 --> 30:58.690
Bring her to me
every seven days before afternoon.

30:58.750 --> 31:00.589
I'll try acupuncture treatment on her.

31:00.590 --> 31:02.930
The rest is up to the heavens.

31:08.590 --> 31:10.650
What we see might not be the truth.

31:10.790 --> 31:13.650
The licorice alone
cannot prove everything.

31:14.910 --> 31:16.650
Still, it's not a baseless observation.

31:16.850 --> 31:18.690
As long as we find
the source of the licorice,

31:19.190 --> 31:20.450
the truth will be revealed.

31:20.510 --> 31:22.870
If we act impulsively,
we might alert our enemies.

31:23.250 --> 31:25.389
The daily necessities
have always been purchased

31:25.390 --> 31:26.730
from regular shops.

31:27.150 --> 31:28.869
For now, if we can obtain

31:28.870 --> 31:30.169
the matching tokens,

31:30.170 --> 31:32.930
we might find something
from the account books.

31:33.640 --> 31:34.949
Why don't we bring Qi Xia

31:34.950 --> 31:36.770
back to Yizhi Hall?

31:37.270 --> 31:39.410
That way, she can get treated,

31:39.550 --> 31:41.970
and after all, she used to work
for the late Duchess,

31:41.990 --> 31:43.530
so she shouldn't be suffering out here.

31:46.150 --> 31:49.850
Perhaps we might discover more.

31:55.750 --> 31:57.050
Didn't you tell me

31:57.150 --> 31:59.050
all those wretched maids
are already dead?

31:59.550 --> 32:01.770
We kept searching,
but we couldn't find her.

32:01.810 --> 32:03.650
Besides, she'd gone mad,

32:03.870 --> 32:05.050
so I thought

32:05.310 --> 32:07.450
her illness had already killed her.

32:07.630 --> 32:08.749
Then, why has she appeared

32:08.750 --> 32:10.770
in Yizhi Hall, alive?

32:10.870 --> 32:12.370
You idiot!

32:14.790 --> 32:15.930
Your Grace!

32:18.350 --> 32:19.930
Get out!

32:28.150 --> 32:35.450
(Lu's Dental Clinic)

32:36.670 --> 32:39.109
If we allow them to investigate further,

32:39.110 --> 32:40.530
they're bound to discover

32:40.610 --> 32:42.410
our involvement as well.

32:43.270 --> 32:45.450
Our spies have reported

32:45.790 --> 32:48.829
that Wang Yingxue is colluding
with the Cangbei Gang,

32:48.830 --> 32:51.509
and they're planning to let
the bandits enter the Capital

32:51.510 --> 32:53.610
to rob Dou Zhao's dowry.

32:53.670 --> 32:56.149
Why don't we distract Song Mo?

32:56.150 --> 32:56.989
So we can...

32:56.990 --> 32:59.810
Dou Zhao is a pawn
to lure Song Mo into our trap.

33:02.230 --> 33:05.490
Are you trying to ruin our plans,
Your Grace?

33:08.390 --> 33:11.090
If this is not a mere robbery,

33:12.070 --> 33:14.380
but a catastrophic event
that could terrorize the capital,

33:15.080 --> 33:18.590
perhaps this is our chance
to regain our military power

33:19.030 --> 33:21.250
and reshuffle the Capital's guards.

33:22.190 --> 33:25.250
His Majesty fell ill today,

33:25.420 --> 33:28.560
and he's about to head to the Western
Mountain Palace for recuperation.

33:28.630 --> 33:32.330
As the commander of the Imperial Guards,

33:32.950 --> 33:34.650
Song Mo will follow him.

33:35.460 --> 33:37.100
The Imperial Guards' duty

33:37.290 --> 33:39.390
is to protect the Emperor.

33:39.600 --> 33:42.890
If he returns to rescue his wife,
he would be betraying His Majesty.

33:43.030 --> 33:44.290
But if he doesn't return,

33:45.040 --> 33:46.960
his wife would be dead.

33:49.010 --> 33:51.180
That's a splendid idea!

33:51.350 --> 33:53.389
No matter what that defiant son decides,

33:53.390 --> 33:55.130
it's a dead end for him.

33:57.150 --> 34:00.290
You're about to destroy
two important pawns in the game.

34:00.470 --> 34:02.570
Don't you feel bad at all,
Grand Secretary Dou?

34:04.710 --> 34:07.730
Dou Zhao is already
part of the Song family.

34:07.990 --> 34:09.610
That's the Duke of Ying's business.

34:10.230 --> 34:11.730
As for Wang Yingxue,

34:12.190 --> 34:14.170
she's always been a pawn,

34:15.030 --> 34:17.530
so it's time for her
to make herself useful.

34:17.590 --> 34:21.970
(Universal Compassion)

34:26.870 --> 34:28.530
This is your reward.

34:30.830 --> 34:31.970
Where's the thing?

34:33.590 --> 34:37.090
(Military Command)

34:43.390 --> 34:44.530
Madam.

34:49.510 --> 34:52.050
(Wei Tingyu)

34:52.550 --> 34:55.210
There's something I don't understand.

34:55.360 --> 34:57.469
Since Cangbei Gang is already helping us

34:57.470 --> 34:58.890
to get rid of Dou Zhao,

34:59.010 --> 35:01.290
why do we need to involve
the Duke of Jining in this?

35:02.350 --> 35:04.530
The Cangbei Gang threatened us

35:04.990 --> 35:07.090
because we couldn't pay our debts.

35:08.350 --> 35:09.890
Everything is caused

35:10.270 --> 35:13.090
by that greedy woman, Wei Tingzhen.

35:13.790 --> 35:14.930
Moreover,

35:15.220 --> 35:17.490
she's also involved
in the money-lending business.

35:18.670 --> 35:21.450
The Duke of Jing is the Empress's family.

35:21.790 --> 35:23.370
Even if their dealings are exposed,

35:23.950 --> 35:26.010
they wouldn't sit by and watch.

35:26.270 --> 35:29.250
Madam, you've planned
everything so well.

35:31.830 --> 35:32.970
Dou Zhao.

35:33.470 --> 35:37.450
No one can save you this time.

35:53.910 --> 35:56.029
Madam, it's a lucky sign!

35:56.030 --> 35:58.290
(No. 24, very lucky)

35:59.790 --> 36:01.530
Thank you for your blessing,
Bodhisattva.

36:02.230 --> 36:06.029
(No. 45, very unlucky)

36:06.030 --> 36:08.810
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

36:15.870 --> 36:19.370
Just stay here
to practice calligraphy tonight.

36:19.550 --> 36:21.690
Don't leave this room.

36:24.710 --> 36:25.850
Father.

36:26.990 --> 36:28.170
What are you up to?

36:29.390 --> 36:30.530
You...

36:30.750 --> 36:32.650
Are you trying to do something
to my brother?

36:33.670 --> 36:35.050
He's my brother!

36:36.230 --> 36:37.370
You fool!

36:37.430 --> 36:38.509
He's a curse

36:38.510 --> 36:40.330
that's been suppressing you!

36:40.830 --> 36:42.069
Now that he's left the capital,

36:42.070 --> 36:43.850
you don't have to worry about him.

36:44.150 --> 36:45.229
Anyway,

36:45.230 --> 36:47.499
no matter what happens tonight,

36:47.500 --> 36:49.530
it's for your future.

36:53.180 --> 36:54.370
Remember.

36:55.270 --> 36:58.450
Keep calm and composed.

36:59.430 --> 37:00.850
Practice well.

37:13.630 --> 37:15.269
Keep an eye on him,

37:15.270 --> 37:18.610
or else you'd be dead too!

37:18.790 --> 37:20.240
Yes, Your Grace.

37:38.290 --> 37:40.519
I've asked around the Capital,

37:40.520 --> 37:42.290
but all of them said
they couldn't fix this.

37:42.910 --> 37:44.050
Mr. Chen.

37:44.230 --> 37:46.810
You said you could fix anything, right?

37:49.400 --> 37:51.610
It's not that I don't want to fix it.

37:51.670 --> 37:53.389
Look how broken it is.

37:53.390 --> 37:55.090
The cracks are too irregular,

37:55.150 --> 37:56.570
and it's made from a rare material.

37:56.650 --> 37:57.810
I really can't

37:58.940 --> 38:00.530
make it done.

38:01.950 --> 38:02.829
Mr. Chen, you know

38:02.830 --> 38:04.389
that I can pay for this.

38:04.390 --> 38:05.810
Help me.

38:06.830 --> 38:09.290
I am a craftsman, not a businessman.

38:10.190 --> 38:11.890
I can't do anything

38:11.950 --> 38:13.610
that might tarnish my reputation.

38:13.630 --> 38:15.490
Mr. Chen.

38:18.300 --> 38:20.830
Take a look around!

38:24.190 --> 38:25.829
Mr. Chen, please try.

38:25.830 --> 38:26.789
Try fixing it, Mr. Chen!

38:26.790 --> 38:27.930
You...

38:28.510 --> 38:29.509
Mr. Chen!

38:29.510 --> 38:30.650
Sit down.

38:32.990 --> 38:34.130
You...

38:44.230 --> 38:45.370
Fu,

38:45.470 --> 38:46.810
where's my office token?

38:47.280 --> 38:48.119
I thought

38:48.120 --> 38:49.889
you carry it with you all the time.

38:49.890 --> 38:51.030
Try searching again.

38:52.470 --> 38:55.170
It's not here. Where is it?

38:55.990 --> 38:57.290
Go back home and search.

38:59.190 --> 39:00.330
Wait.

39:07.990 --> 39:09.930
Forget it, I'll go back
and search myself.

39:11.510 --> 39:12.650
It's the Duke!

39:15.390 --> 39:16.530
Youming.

39:17.350 --> 39:19.930
Are you going to sell your paintings?

39:20.910 --> 39:22.109
Oh, no.

39:22.110 --> 39:24.269
I'm heading to the Military Command.

39:24.270 --> 39:26.170
I'm on duty today.

39:26.670 --> 39:28.290
Why don't you join us for a drink?

39:29.350 --> 39:31.149
A drink? But I...

39:31.150 --> 39:32.309
No more buts.

39:32.310 --> 39:34.629
Everyone knows that your mother-in-law

39:34.630 --> 39:37.010
got you a boring, useless job.

39:39.610 --> 39:42.389
I invited a few senior officials
from the Military Command to join us.

39:42.390 --> 39:44.450
They can help your
career progression, see?

39:45.110 --> 39:46.650
- This way.
- Come on.

39:47.270 --> 39:48.349
Let's go.

39:48.350 --> 39:49.490
This way.

39:49.950 --> 39:51.090
Come on.

39:51.430 --> 39:54.730
(Yizhi Hall Account Book)

39:58.770 --> 40:00.370
There's a fire over there!

40:00.650 --> 40:01.790
Fire!

40:01.980 --> 40:03.170
Near the gates!

40:04.990 --> 40:06.130
Su Xin.

40:09.890 --> 40:11.209
What's with the commotion outside?

40:11.210 --> 40:12.760
There's a fire
outside the residence.

40:12.770 --> 40:14.250
I've already checked it out.

40:15.190 --> 40:16.370
A fire?

40:19.390 --> 40:22.509
(Natural Grace and Talent)

40:22.510 --> 40:23.650
Your Ladyship,

40:24.190 --> 40:25.489
there's a fire at the North Gate.

40:25.490 --> 40:27.010
The fire is getting serious,

40:27.270 --> 40:28.770
so we've already sent a request

40:28.790 --> 40:30.170
to the Military Command.

40:30.370 --> 40:32.970
Someone should be here soon
to extinguish the flames.

40:33.470 --> 40:34.650
That looks serious.

40:34.670 --> 40:36.629
I don't think we can wait

40:36.630 --> 40:37.850
till they arrive.

40:38.870 --> 40:41.229
General Yan, take some men with you
to put the fire out.

40:41.230 --> 40:43.330
His Lordship has ordered me

40:43.390 --> 40:45.370
to stay here and protect you.

40:45.870 --> 40:46.869
Don't worry.

40:46.870 --> 40:47.960
If His Lordship were here,

40:47.970 --> 40:49.530
he would've asked you to do the same.

40:49.550 --> 40:51.850
Besides, I still have Mr. Chen,

40:52.030 --> 40:53.170
Su Xin, and Su Lan with me.

40:53.270 --> 40:54.109
Go and help them.

40:54.110 --> 40:55.290
If that's what you wish.

40:57.390 --> 41:00.389
You guys stay here and
protect Her Ladyship.

41:00.390 --> 41:01.349
As for the others, follow me!

41:01.350 --> 41:02.490
- Yes, General!
- Yes, General!

41:09.110 --> 41:10.229
What's your business here?

41:10.230 --> 41:11.149
Sir.

41:11.150 --> 41:13.680
I have been ordered to clear the road
for the imperial carriage.

41:14.670 --> 41:16.770
(Military Command)

41:18.070 --> 41:19.210
Open the gates!

41:19.770 --> 41:21.169
- You may enter.
- Thank you, sir.

41:21.170 --> 41:22.310
Let's go.

41:27.230 --> 41:28.349
Hold it!

41:28.350 --> 41:29.730
What's on the wagon?

42:01.070 --> 42:03.290
That's very treacherous of you.

42:03.430 --> 42:04.709
That woman named Dou Zhao

42:04.710 --> 42:06.669
has tens of thousands of gold taels.

42:06.670 --> 42:08.010
Are you trying to keep

42:08.070 --> 42:09.450
all the bounty to yourself?

42:10.550 --> 42:12.780
Even the imperial treasury
doesn't have that much money.

42:13.070 --> 42:14.000
Who told you that?

42:14.010 --> 42:15.109
That's none of your concern.

42:15.110 --> 42:16.280
You can take Yizhi Hall,

42:16.290 --> 42:18.229
but I'm taking all the shops
and food warehouses

42:18.230 --> 42:19.109
at the North Gates!

42:19.110 --> 42:20.250
Move it!

42:20.870 --> 42:21.869
Boss, this is...

42:21.870 --> 42:22.869
Make this a quick battle.

42:22.870 --> 42:24.010
Go!

42:45.710 --> 42:46.850
Your Majesty.

42:47.090 --> 42:49.290
Lord Song, what is it?

42:49.300 --> 42:51.010
I have something urgent
to report.

42:51.020 --> 42:52.490
Please pass my message.

42:52.790 --> 42:54.410
His Majesty has just taken his medicine,

42:54.470 --> 42:56.010
and he's finally getting some rest.

42:56.150 --> 42:58.410
Anything can wait till morning.

42:58.420 --> 43:00.499
I noticed that the Capital
seemed to be lit up in flames.

43:00.500 --> 43:01.589
Something terrible must have happened.

43:01.590 --> 43:03.210
- I don't think we can wait.
- Lord Song.

43:03.590 --> 43:06.290
As the Emperor's servant, you should
be sharing His Majesty's burden.

43:06.430 --> 43:08.970
Right now, our priority
is to help His Majesty recuperate.

43:09.110 --> 43:10.029
Moreover,

43:10.030 --> 43:12.290
the Military Command
will protect the capital.

43:13.350 --> 43:16.210
Your sole responsibility
is to protect His Majesty.

43:34.830 --> 43:37.869
(Jieyi Hall)

43:37.870 --> 43:39.109
Someone opened the West Gate!

43:39.110 --> 43:40.469
The bandits are rushing in!

43:40.470 --> 43:42.029
If those bandits dare to come here,

43:42.030 --> 43:44.410
I'll make sure
they'll never leave here again.

43:44.430 --> 43:45.850
Hey, lady.

43:45.990 --> 43:47.410
Let's see where you can go.

43:48.030 --> 43:49.170
You wretch!

43:50.690 --> 43:53.329
♪The lingering uncertainty
has yet been resolved♪

43:53.330 --> 43:57.809
♪I gaze at you, and all is calm♪

43:57.810 --> 44:01.570
♪The world is vast and turbulent♪

44:01.730 --> 44:06.120
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

44:06.300 --> 44:10.229
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

44:10.230 --> 44:13.209
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

44:13.210 --> 44:15.419
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

44:15.420 --> 44:17.980
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

44:18.030 --> 44:21.600
♪Your presence by
my side is irreplaceable♪

44:21.660 --> 44:25.180
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

44:25.190 --> 44:29.169
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

44:29.170 --> 44:33.200
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:33.640 --> 44:37.100
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:37.260 --> 44:39.440
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:39.460 --> 44:43.290
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:43.620 --> 44:46.760
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:47.300 --> 44:50.710
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:51.150 --> 44:54.690
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:54.890 --> 44:58.559
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:58.560 --> 45:02.900
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

45:02.960 --> 45:06.689
♪Having you is a blessing♪

45:06.690 --> 45:10.169
♪Only by being by your side♪

45:10.170 --> 45:14.850
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

45:14.880 --> 45:18.469
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

45:18.470 --> 45:22.610
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

45:22.680 --> 45:25.970
♪Always together, looking back♪

45:26.280 --> 45:33.580
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:42.830 --> 45:43.869
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama.)

45:43.870 --> 45:44.829
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:44.830 --> 45:46.050
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home.)
